n --ci-testing <formulae>` nightly to test that the brew formulas are working fine. Specially useful since it can detect if we lack a bottle or there are some other problems.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Inspiration from <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/release-tools/pull-requests/167/brew-bottles-creation-and-hash-updating/activity#comment-13739923\" rel=\"nofollow\">this @scpeters comment</a>.</p>\n<p>Basically run <code>brew test-bot --tap=osrf/simulation --ci-testing &lt;formulae&gt;</code> nightly to test that the brew formulas are working fine. Specially useful since it can detect if we lack a bottle or there are some other problems.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2016-04-06T22:14:17.943660+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2017-05-04T21:06:17.021466+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 66}